### POST /paymentmanagement/rest/getCardTokenSecure

This endpoint is used to retrieve a secure token for a credit card.

#### Request

- Method: POST

- URL: `https://omccstb.turkcell.com.tr/paymentmanagement/rest/getCardTokenSecure`

- Headers:

    - Content-Type: application/json

